Interface IOstoslistaDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OstoslistaDAO

    public interface IOstoslistaDAO
    The IOstoslistaDAO interface provides all the methods necessary for communicating with the Ostoslista table in the database.

    ville

      • createOstoslista

        boolean createOstoslista(double maara,
                         int tuote_id)
        For creating a new record in the Ostoslista table.
        Parameters:
        maara - The amount of the Tuote being placed in the Ostoslista.
        tuote_id - The ID of the Tuote being placed in the fridge.
        Returns:
        Returns true if the new record was created successfully into the database.

        Returns:
        Returns the Ostoslista record form the database which was read.

      • readOstoslistaId

      • readOstoslistaName

        For reading all the Ostoslista record from the database with the matching Tuote name.
